data.text: @lasc1943 This is definitely the Parental Alienation Syndrome. It's harmful to children and will scare them emotionally for life. Angelina Jolie should know that.
@lasc1943 I feel really bad for the kids. Her mom did it to Jon Voight, her and her brother hate him. All this is to create problems for the kids that will carry the rest of their lives.
